{"article_id":"FUFEijwoBwLuvgja","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The NBA finds itself caught between two cultures","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"after a tweet about Hong Kong protests sparked criticism from China","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"that threatens the U.S. basketball league ' s expansion efforts in its most important international market .","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"The controversy erupted","depth":12},{"id":4,"text":"after Daryl Morey , general manager of the Houston Rockets , one of the most popular U.S. basketball teams in China , appeared to support Hong Kong demonstrators in a tweet late Friday .","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"While the message was deleted","depth":13},{"id":6,"text":"and both Morey and the National Basketball Association tried to distance themselves from it ,","depth":13},{"id":7,"text":"the damage reverberated across both China and the U.S .","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"For the Chinese , the incident is seen as the latest example of a Western organization","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"challenging the nation ' s sovereignty over its territory .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"In the U.S. , meanwhile , the NBA ' s response was met with scorching bipartisan criticism from politicians","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"including Senator Ted Cruz .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"The situation puts the league at risk","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"of either offending fans in its biggest international market ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"or exposing itself to charges","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"of kowtowing to China at the expense of American values .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"\" Chinese Rockets fans are first Chinese .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"We love Chinese red more than Rockets red , \"","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"Kang Hui , an anchor for CCTV News Channel , said in a video on an official CCTV Weibo account .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"\" Morey , this time you really fouled .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"If you foul ,","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"you have to pay the price . \"","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"At stake is a business","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that has been notching double-digit growth in China every year since 2008 .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"The league has achieved the kind of success there","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that other international sports leagues covet .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"About 800 million Chinese watch NBA programming on TV , digital media or smartphones in a season ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"with top games attracting more viewers than in the U.S .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"The NBA has a host of licensing and retail deals in China ,","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"including a $ 500 million pact with Tencent Holdings Ltd. and a 30-plus-years partnership with state-run broadcaster CCTV .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Tencent has seen Internet viewership of NBA games nearly triple over the past four years .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"The fallout was swift","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"following Morey ' s tweet ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"which contained an image","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that read","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" Fight for Freedom .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Stand with Hong Kong. \"","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Chinese sportswear maker Li Ning Co. and Shanghai Pudong Development Bank Credit Card Center suspended cooperation with the Rockets ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"while CCTV and Tencent said","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"they will halt broadcasting the team ' s games .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"Searches for Rockets gear on Chinese e-commerce sites","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"operated by JD.com Inc. and Alibaba Group Holding Ltd.","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"didn ' t return any results on Monday .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"1/ I did not intend my tweet to cause any offense to Rockets fans and friends of mine in China .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"I was merely voicing one thought ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"based on one interpretation ,","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"of one complicated event .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"I have had a lot of opportunity since that tweet","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to hear and consider other perspectives .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"- Daryl Morey","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"( @ dmorey )","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"October 7 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"2/ I have always appreciated the significant support","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"our Chinese fans and sponsors have provided","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and I would hope","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"that those","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"who are upset","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"will know","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that offending or misunderstanding them was not my intention .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"My tweets are my own","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"and in no way represent the Rockets or the NBA .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"- Daryl Morey","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"( @ dmorey )","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"October 7 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"The NBA is just the latest international business","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"feeling the heat from the standoff between pro-democracy demonstrators and Hong Kong authorities","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"that has escalated since June .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"From Starbucks Corp. to Cathay Pacific Airways Ltd. , brands and companies are being targeted","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"if they ' re seen to be supporting either side in the dispute .","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"Get The Brief .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Sign up","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"to receive the top stories","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"you need to know right now .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Choose your country","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"United States of America","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Afghanistan Albania","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Algeria","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"American Samoa Andorra","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Angola Anguilla Antigua and Barbuda","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Argentina Armenia","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Aruba","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Australia Austria","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Azerbaijan Bahamas","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"Bahrain","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"Bangladesh Barbados Belarus Belgium Belize Benin Bermuda Bhutan Bolivia Bosnia and Herzegovina Botswana Brazil Brunei Darussalam Bulgaria Burkina Faso Burundi","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"Cambodia Cameroon","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"Canada","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"Cape Verde","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"Cayman Islands","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"Central African Republic","depth":15},{"id":90,"text":"Chad","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"Chile China Colombia Comoros","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"Congo Congo , Democratic Republic of Cook Islands","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"Costa Rica","depth":18},{"id":94,"text":"Cote d'Ivoire","depth":20},{"id":95,"text":"Croatia Cuba","depth":21},{"id":96,"text":"Cyprus","depth":22},{"id":97,"text":"Czech Republic Denmark","depth":23},{"id":98,"text":"Djibouti Dominica Dominican Republic Ecuador Egypt El Salvador Equatorial Guinea Eritrea Estonia Ethiopia","depth":23},{"id":99,"text":"Faeroe Islands","depth":19},{"id":100,"text":"Falkland Islands","depth":19},{"id":101,"text":"( Malvinas )","depth":19},{"id":102,"text":"Fiji Finland France French Guiana","depth":20},{"id":103,"text":"French Polynesia","depth":21},{"id":104,"text":"Gabon Gambia Georgia Germany Ghana Gibraltar Greece Greenland Grenada Guadeloupe Guam Guatemala Guinea Guinea-Bissau Guyana Haiti","depth":21},{"id":105,"text":"Holy See Honduras Hong Kong Hungary Iceland India Indonesia Iran Iraq Ireland Israel Italy Jamaica Japan Jordan Kazakhstan Kenya Kiribati Korea Kuwait Kyrgyzstan Laos Latvia Lebanon Lesotho Liberia Libyan Arab Jamahiriya Liechtenstein Lithuania Luxembourg Macao Macedonia Madagascar Malawi Malaysia Maldives","depth":22},{"id":106,"text":"Mali Malta Marshall Islands",